{"tid":1955036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 港台訪問世衛高層內容有違「一個中國」原則 港台總編輯必須對此負責","createTime":"2020-04-02T08:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T12:01:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7e493ef19915b03993f40624a4acc97cdd37b8","tid":1955036,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"商經局指港台訪問世衛高層內容有違「一個中國」原則<br />\n02.04.2020 16:12<br />\n香港電台英文台早前視像訪問世界衛生組織助理總幹事艾爾沃德，期間問及台灣的世衛成員資格，艾爾沃德表示聽不到問題，再被追問後線路中斷。商務及經濟發展局發言人指，局長邱騰華認為有關節目有違「一個中國」原則及《香港電台約章》中訂明的目的和使命，又指世衛組織成員國均以主權國家為單位，作為政府部門和公共廣播機構，港台必須對此有正確認識，廣播處長作為港台總編輯必須對此負責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n局方又指，港台必須恪守和按照《香港電台約章》，提供讓市民了解社會和國家的節目，培養市民對公民及國民身份的認同感，以及增加市民對「一國兩制」的認識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278332&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278332%26csid%3D261_341&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMn9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=c4d8f65d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278332&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9725c5d2f1c1eab2d3e33b02e9f92e42253a4b12","tid":1955036,"uid":34553,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"食屎啦商經局"},{"pid":"58ac70c32c2efa3ef7334c5a6e04a3262eae2acc","tid":1955036,"uid":283207,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"港台好肉酸真係搞分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbaeab135a16ab6652e69d508308e0621636315","tid":1955036,"uid":34553,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"58ac70c32c2efa3ef7334c5a6e04a3262eae2acc","tid":1955036,"uid":283207,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"港台